name: Somette_Grey_Weathered_2-Door_Cabinet
reviews: Purchased the Somette Grey 2-door cabinet as an accent piece for my living room. Shipped quickly and arrived well packaged. The piece itself is gorgeous. Color and description were as stated on Overstock. This piece is solid and well built, not to mention gorgeous. The color compliments my weathered grey hardwood and I couldn't be happier.
description: Accent your home's decor with this stylish Somette cabinet. The grey/ blue color and painted finish, distressed of this rectangle cabinet will bring a refined feel to your home. Made of MDF and wood, this cabinet has a solid construction built to last.
